<tool_call>
{
  "tool": "data_processing_validator",
  "parameters": {
    "schema": {
      "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": true
    },
    "data": {},
    "options": {}
  }
}
</tool_call>

I need to handle the validation failure. Since the validator requires a schema and we don't know the data structure, I'll first parse the data to understand its structure. According to the workflow plan, the next tool should be data_processing_parser.

<tool_call>
{
  "tool": "data_processing_parser",
  "parameters": {
    "source": "https://api.example.com/data",
    "options": {}
  }
}
</tool_call>

